    "media:imagetext": "W\nREDCLUB\nPan Am WorldClub bonus\nsectors for second\nquarter, 1983.\nPan Am has announced its bonus sectors for\nthe second quarter. Each of the city pairs\ndesignated below earns Pan Am WorldClub\nmembers bonus points toward travel on\nPan Am.\nThese bonus sectors are valid for second-\nquarter. Subsequent issues of the Pan Am\nWorldClub Quarterly will outline new bonus\nsectors for each quarter.\nEvery Pan Am Sector Sold\n1 Basic Point\nPlus:\nSell First Class and earn 2 premium points\nSell Clipper Class and earn 1 premium point\n2 Bonus Points\nEach Way\nbetween\nNew York or\nMiami\nand\nRio de Janeiro or\nBuenos Aires\n2 Bonus Points\nEach Way\nbetween\nNew York\nLos Angeles\nSan Francisco or\nHonolulu\nand\nTokyo\nHong Kong or\nSingapore\n1 Bonus Point\nEach Way\nbetween\nany Pan Am U.S. City\nand\nLondon\n1 Bonus Point\nEach Way\nbetween\nSan Francisco\nand\nNew York\n+W\n0334\n1 Bonus Point\nEach Way\nbetween\nSan Francisco\nand\nHouston\nDallas or\nNew Orleans\nWCII02",
