    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "W\nRIDCLUB\nU\nR\nT\nE\nR\nVolume 1, Number 1 April, 1983\nL\nY\nREDCR\nPan Am\nInaugurates\nWorldClub.\nChairman announces the most re-\nwarding organization in the world\nfor professional travel counselors.\nC. Edward Acker, Chairman of\nPan American World Airways, Inc. has\nannounced the formation of Pan Am\nWorldClub,* an exclusive club that\noffers professional travel counselors the\nopportunity to earn points good towards\nfree travel on Pan Am.\n\"Pan Am has long recognized the\nessential role professional travel coun\nhave been pleased in the past to acknowl-\nedge their contributions and to applaud\ntheir accomplishments. We're especially\npleased to be able to offer them member-\nship in our new Pan Am WorldClub.\"\nAs outlined by Mr. Acker, Pan Am\nWorldClub membership is open to quali-\nfied professional travel counselors\nactively engaged in selling travel to the\npublic and employed by selected accred-\nited ATC and lATA travel agencies.\nPan Am WorldClub members will be\njoining \"the most knowledgeable and\nprotessional group of men and women in\nthe travel industry today.\"",
      "W\nREDCLUB\nPan Am WorldClub bonus\nsectors for second\nquarter, 1983.\nPan Am has announced its bonus sectors for\nthe second quarter. Each of the city pairs\ndesignated below earns Pan Am WorldClub\nmembers bonus points toward travel on\nPan Am.\nThese bonus sectors are valid for second-\nquarter. Subsequent issues of the Pan Am\nWorldClub Quarterly will outline new bonus\nsectors for each quarter.\nEvery Pan Am Sector Sold\n1 Basic Point\nPlus:\nSell First Class and earn 2 premium points\nSell Clipper Class and earn 1 premium point\n2 Bonus Points\nEach Way\nbetween\nNew York or\nMiami\nand\nRio de Janeiro or\nBuenos Aires\n2 Bonus Points\nEach Way\nbetween\nNew York\nLos Angeles\nSan Francisco or\nHonolulu\nand\nTokyo\nHong Kong or\nSingapore\n1 Bonus Point\nEach Way\nbetween\nany Pan Am U.S. City\nand\nLondon\n1 Bonus Point\nEach Way\nbetween\nSan Francisco\nand\nNew York\n+W\n0334\n1 Bonus Point\nEach Way\nbetween\nSan Francisco\nand\nHouston\nDallas or\nNew Orleans\nWCII02"
    ],
